# ============================================================
# Nomade Drive Brasil — repository ignore list
# ============================================================

# --- Source / raw materials (NOT deployed to the site) ---
Imagens/
Imagens brand-logo/
Imagens Uberlandia/

# --- Internal financial / planning spreadsheets ---
# (keep Contrato_NomadDrive.xlsx — it's downloadable from the site)
Simulador_Viabilidade_NomadDrive.xlsx

# --- Helper scripts (used once to build assets, no need to ship) ---
_*.py
_*.js

# --- Mirror folder for Netlify Drop (we use Vercel now from root) ---
publicar/

# --- Test artifacts ---
node_modules/
*.log

# --- Segredos / variáveis de ambiente ---
# NUNCA versionar a service_role key nem arquivos .env reais.
# A anon key fica em supabase-config.js (é pública e protegida por RLS).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
supabase-secrets.*

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Editor configs ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.claude.json
# Pastas locais de notas e backup
INBOX_COWORKER/
Imagens parceiros/
Novas atualizacoes 6 arquivos/
Testes QA/
